                <ol class="steps">  
                    <li>
                        <b style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;">1. Registration</b>
                        <ul>
                            <li> <i class="fa fa-circle" style="color: #b99663; font-size: 11px; margin: 11px 13px 0px 0px;"></i> Click <b>"Admission"</b> menu and select <b>"New Registration"</b> sub-menu.</li>
                            <li><i class="fa fa-circle" style="color: #b99663; font-size: 11px; margin: 11px 13px 0px 0px;"></i>Fill in all details such as username, password, email, etc., and click on <b>"Create my new account"</b> button. You will get an email to your registered email-id with the Activation/Verification Link. You need to click/open the verification link in order to activate your account.
                                <br>Note: You may receive activation link in your spam folder sometime. Please check if you have not received it in Inbox.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <b style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;">2. Login</b>
                        <ul>
                            <li><i class="fa fa-circle" style="color: #b99663; font-size: 11px; margin: 11px 13px 0px 0px;"></i>Go to <b>"Admission"</b> menu and Select <b>"Apply Online"</b>. You will be directed to the Application Dashboard if you already logged in. Otherwise you will be directed to <b>"Login"</b> form to login with your credential.</li>
                            <li><i class="fa fa-circle" style="color: #b99663; font-size: 11px; margin: 11px 13px 0px 0px;"></i>If you are the existing user, Go to <b">Admission"</b> menu and Select <b>"Applicant Login"</b>. You will be directed to <b>"Login"</b> form to login with your credential.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <b style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;">3. Application Form Entry</b>
                        <ul>
                            <li><i class="fa fa-circle" style="color: #b99663; font-size: 11px; margin: 11px 13px 0px 0px;"></i>Click <b>"Apply Here"</b> to start filling your application. You need to fill-in all the required fields and upload the necessary documents/certificates in proper format and size. Once you filled-in all the fields, then proceed to the next step.</li>
                            <li><i class="fa fa-circle" style="color: #b99663; font-size: 11px; margin: 11px 13px 0px 0px;"></i>Click <b>"View & Submit Application"</b> in order to verify your application. If all the details are correct, then select <b>"Confirm Submission"</b> and Click <b>"Submit"</b>. If there are corrections to be made, then click <b>"Edit Application"</b> and update your application details.
                                <br><b>"Please note that once the form is submitted, you will not be able to edit afterwards."</b></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <b style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;">4.Payment</b>
                        <ul>
                            <li><i class="fa fa-circle" style="color: #b99663; font-size: 11px; margin: 11px 13px 0px 0px;"></i>Click <b>"Payment"</b> to pay for the application fees. Then click <b>"Pay now"</b> to make the payment via Credit Card/Debit Card/Net banking/UPI. On successful payment, your application will be generated with an application number. Download the application for later reference.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
